<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="logo logged-in"></div>
    <div class="col s12">
      <div class="card purple lighten-5">
        <div class="card-content">
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
            Welcome back,  <strong><%= current_user.email %></strong>
            <%# <%= link_to "Edit profile", edit_user_registration_path, :class => "navbar-link" %>
            <%= link_to "(logout)", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, :class => "navbar-link"  %>

            <!-- @TODO should show Card.all with a button for creating new, not rendering the form -->
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m12 l6">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-content">
          <h3>My Cards</h3>
          <p>To share these with your friends, click the button to copy the link and simply send that to them.</p>
          <br />
          <p>Each person to use the link will have a fresh card randomly generated for them. They don't need to even sign up or sign in!
          </p>
          <table class="card-table">
            <tbody>
              <% @cards.each do |card| %>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p class="bingo-card-title"><%= link_to card.title, edit_card_path(card) %><p>
                    <h4>
                      <a href="/<%= card.url %>" class="btn cyan lighten-2 black-text share-url">
                        <i class="material-icons left">content_copy</i>
                        click to copy
                      </a>
                    </h4>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              <% end %>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <ul class="btn-list">
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m12 l6">
      <div class="card cyan lighten-5">
        <div class="card-content">
          <h3>Create a Bingo Card?</h3>
          <p>If you haven't created a card yet start here. You will be asked to fill out at least 75 terms to keep the game fun and exciting.</p>
          <br />
          <a href="/cards/new" class="btn yellow black-text waves-effect waves-light"><i class="material-icons left">add_box</i>Create Bingo Card!</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
